{"tid":1418731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發完夢之後小小感想","createTime":"2019-08-05T20:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T20:20:53.000Z","uid":23989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8bad1bf422e45a0fe2bdacef1c95f718c8171ec0","tid":1418731,"uid":23989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:03:40.000Z","msg":"唔好自己一個發 <br />\n就算得返自己一個 真係唔好怕羞 <br />\n試下埋堆 不如一齊發夢<br />\n 2~3個人貼緊小小行就好足夠<br />\n<br />\n三個臭皮匠，勝過一個諸葛亮<br />\n<br />\n如果聽到前線講到明快閃邊度邊度<br />\n大家真係想加入 就行快d 跟快d<br />\n出現左一個情況就係第一批快閃完<br />\n見到出黑色 諗住走 <br />\n第2批先到<br />\n開始有不同意見<br />\n第3批人已經比風向帶走左<br />\n講得快閃 <br />\n跟到就跟 跟唔到就留係到<br />\n你留係到仲有好多作用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只係希望大家以後可以發個好夢<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9db6475ea988925732c244f3692a0e4277b28c","tid":1418731,"uid":23989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:12:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751a8a1d00d9f3410619c66c86f80d814645f487","tid":1418731,"uid":23989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}